Class TemplateRoutineBuilder<IN,OUT>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.github.dm.jrt.core.TemplateRoutine<IN,OUT>
      • com.github.dm.jrt.builder.TemplateRoutineBuilder<IN,OUT>
  • Type Parameters:
    IN - the input data type.
    OUT - the output data type.
    All Implemented Interfaces:
    ConfigurableBuilder<RoutineBuilder<IN,OUT>>, InvocationConfiguration.Configurable<RoutineBuilder<IN,OUT>>, RoutineBuilder<IN,OUT>, Routine<IN,OUT>

    public abstract class TemplateRoutineBuilder<IN,OUT>
extends TemplateRoutine<IN,OUT>
implements RoutineBuilder<IN,OUT>, InvocationConfiguration.Configurable<RoutineBuilder<IN,OUT>>
    Empty abstract implementation of a routine builder.

    This class is useful to avoid the need of implementing some of the methods defined in the interface.

    Created by davide-maestroni on 03/16/2015.
